Interface IAgentListener

public interface IAgentListener

Interface for external processes that want to be notified on certain agent events.

Method Detail

agentTerminating

void agentTerminating(AgentEvent ae)
Called when the agent is closing down (i.e. moving to the end state). In this state the agent should perform cleanup operations and is still able to execute goals/plans as well as send/receive messages.

Parameters:
ae - The agent event.
